I'm now incorporating the UI provided directly into the `App.tsx` component, including the conditional display of the notification status and the "Enable Alerts" button. I'm focusing on integrating this specific component into the sidebar and correctly handling the different permission states within `App.tsx` to match the display as requested. I've updated the code and am integrating the blocks as requested.


